=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
$)

  $( Axiom of Existence.  One of the equality and substitution axioms of
     predicate calculus with equality.  This axiom tells us is that at least
     one thing exists.  In this form (not requiring that ` x ` and ` y ` be
