       ~ http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/aristotle-logic/ , and
       ~ https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syllogism .  (Contributed by David A.
       Wheeler, 24-Aug-2016.) $)
    barbara $p |- A. x ( ch -> ps ) $=
